# ONRG Order now
web app to order food online

### Features
User can signup for an account and order food once they log in.
Dishes gets added to their cart and payment can be made via card.
Responsive web pages that enable users to use app on mobile phones.
User can contact the cafe owner by filling in contact form.
Gallery have photos for all the dishes in the menu.

### Technologies used
Javascript , Ruby , Sinatra , HTML , CSS , ActiveRecord , Postgres , SQL


### Heroku (Deployed app)
